	* signal.c (ruby_signal): don't set SA_RESTART.  a backport from
	  the HEAD.  [ruby-talk:220937]  [ruby-talk:147220]

	* signal.c (Init_signal): avoid duplicated installation of SIGCHLD
	  handler.

