	* ext/tk/lib/multi-tk.rb: fail to call function-style methods on slave
	  interpreters. The strategy (MultiTkIp_PseudoToplevel_Evaluable) to
	  fix the problem is a little tricky. You may have to take care of
	  conflicting with it.

