	  fixed: [ruby-dev:26881]

Tue Sep 13 16:26:45 2005  Minero Aoki  <aamine@loveruby.net>

	* lib/net/http.rb: backported from trunk, rev 1.128.
	  [ruby-dev:25673] [ruby-dev:26617]

