	* lib/pathname.rb (realpath): make ELOOP check bit more robust.
	  (children): prepend self by default.
	  (chroot): obsoleted.

Tue Oct 14 02:29:31 2003  Nobuyoshi Nakada  <nobu@ruby-lang.org>

	* eval.c (rb_require_safe): segfault after loading .so.

