Wed Sep 17 18:03:30 2003  GOTOU Yuuzou  <gotoyuzo@notwork.org>

	* ext/openssl: all files are reviewed to simplify and avoid memory leak.

	* ext/openssl/extconf.rb: add check for assert.h.

